                            <comment id="17709423" author="JIRAUSER298945" created="Thu, 6 Apr 2023 15:02:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In conclusion, I haven&apos;t found any deadlocks or other suspicious things. I was able to reproduce it locally it seems it indeed just works pretty slowly on an overloaded machine. So I just increased the timeout. We will see how it will be.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;merged to master: 6e95bfaf&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17726522" author="sergey nuyanzin" created="Fri, 26 May 2023 08:17:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged to 1.16 as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/141b47a80092134f95dfdf6b3d0e7051d4fec6bb&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;141b47a80092134f95dfdf6b3d0e7051d4fec6bb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
